Insurers are leaving. Companies are fleeing. Doctors are quitting. It's an absolute disaster. Hillary Clinton wants to double-down on Obamacare and make it even worse. She wants to put the government totally in charge of your healthcare. Repealing Obamacare, and stopping Hillary's healthcare takeover, is one of the single most important reasons we must win on November 8th.

